# Running the project
When running the project, the working directory must contain a directory "data" containing the dataset and the embeddings file.

To train the model according to a specific experiment and compute the perplexities on the test set:
python3 model.py --experiment [A|B|C]

To compute the perplexities on the test set, using a pre-trained model saved at the "result" directory:
python3 model.py --experiment [A|B|C] --perplexity_only

To generate sentences continuing those on the continuation file, using a pre-trained model saved at the "result" directory:
python3 model.py --experiment C --sentence_generation
